The build fails because of the **ESLint errors** (not warnings). Only this file is blocking the build:

**`src/components/ui/lucide.tsx` line 11** — unescaped `"` characters.

Fix it by escaping the quotes:

```tsx
// Before (line 11 - something like):
"icon name"
// After:
&ldquo;icon name&rdquo;
// Or use curly braces:
{"\"icon name\""}
```

The warnings (`<img>`, `useEffect` deps) won't block the build.

**Quick fix without seeing the file:**

```bash
sed -i 's/"/\&quot;/g' src/components/ui/lucide.tsx
```

Or if you want to suppress lint errors temporarily to unblock the build, add to `next.config.mjs`:

```js
eslint: {
  ignoreDuringBuilds: true,
},
```

But the proper fix is escaping those quotes in `lucide.tsx` line 11.
